1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:03,894
A transcript is more than a block of text.

2
00:00:03,894 --> 00:00:08,132
Before import, confirm that the study permits this storage location,

3
00:00:08,132 --> 00:00:12,369
remove direct identifiers where appropriate and use synthetic material whenever

4
00:00:12,369 --> 00:00:14,912
you are only learning the interface.

5
00:00:15,312 --> 00:00:20,090
The public guide explains the supported source workflow and current limits.

6
00:00:20,090 --> 00:00:24,434
Review it before a large import so file types, transcript

7
00:00:24,434 --> 00:00:28,344
length and plan limits do not interrupt the study.

8
00:00:28,744 --> 00:00:30,870
In the workspace, open Transcript.

9
00:00:30,870 --> 00:00:35,123
Choose the path that matches your material, give the source

10
00:00:35,123 --> 00:00:39,375
a useful title and keep participant identifiers out of the

11
00:00:39,375 --> 00:00:42,352
title unless the protocol explicitly allows them.

12
00:00:42,752 --> 00:00:45,843
The Sources tab provides a compact inventory.

13
00:00:45,843 --> 00:00:50,259
Use it to confirm that each interview arrived once, spot

14
00:00:50,259 --> 00:00:54,675
naming inconsistencies and return to a particular source without searching

15
00:00:54,675 --> 00:00:56,000
the whole canvas.

16
00:00:56,400 --> 00:01:01,256
Open the transcript node and read around each passage before coding.

17
00:01:01,256 --> 00:01:05,671
Qualitative meaning depends on context, so avoid creating a code

18
00:01:05,671 --> 00:01:10,085
from a highlighted phrase alone when the surrounding answer changes

19
00:01:10,085 --> 00:01:10,968
its interpretation.

20
00:01:11,368 --> 00:01:17,306
For real participant material, align QualCanvas with the consent form,

21
00:01:17,306 --> 00:01:20,275
ethics approval and institutional policy.

22
00:01:20,275 --> 00:01:26,213
The privacy page documents retention, deletion, portability and service-provider locations;

23
00:01:26,213 --> 00:01:29,776
your protocol remains the controlling boundary.

24
00:01:30,176 --> 00:01:35,053
The safe habit is straightforward: check permission, remove unnecessary identifiers,

25
00:01:35,053 --> 00:01:39,442
name the source clearly and verify the import once.

26
00:01:39,442 --> 00:01:42,368
Then you are ready to code.
